# Static analysis — finish checklist

## When to run

After Java, SQL, or config changes. Skip docs-only / `.mdc`-only edits.

## Required commands (match CI)

```bash
./mvnw -B clean test
```

## Formatting

```bash
./mvnw -B process-sources
```

Uses [`resources/formatter.xml`](../../resources/formatter.xml) — [passport-format-imports.mdc](passport-format-imports.mdc).

## IDE diagnostics

`ReadLints` on changed files; fix new issues.

## Do not finish while

- `./mvnw test` fails.
- New linter problems in touched files.
